Requirements:
	Mandatory:
•	Program must be capable of displaying a ball that “bounces” around the screen
•	Ball must be able to detect edges of screen and “bounce” off of them
•	Program must allow user draw obstacles on screen
•	Program must identify obstacles on screen drawn by the player greater than 3 pixels in size
•	Program must be able to have ball react to obstacles drawn by player
Optional:
•	Program may allow users to import a background image
•	Program may allow users to change color of drawing tool
•	Program may allow users to adjust thickness of drawing tool
•	Program may contain an undo functions
•	Program may contain a redo function
•	Program may allow a user to drop a ball from a certain point on the screen
